
Module 'genome/lib' has scripts called internally by 'genome' - these are not 
called by an end user.
    
-------------------------------------------------------------------
get.sh
-------------------------------------------------------------------

Download genome reference files from UCSC.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
fasta.sh
-------------------------------------------------------------------

Create and index a single FASTA file containing only the canonical chromosomes,
and index the RefSeq mRNA FASTA file, if present.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
gap.sh
-------------------------------------------------------------------

Create a BED file containing the genome gaps.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
transcripts.sh
-------------------------------------------------------------------

Create a BED file of transcript spans.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
genes.sh
-------------------------------------------------------------------

Create a BED file of gene spans.

-------------------------------------------------------------------
map.pl
-------------------------------------------------------------------

Create collapsed stranded and unstranded transcriptome maps.  See script
for details.

